is methods and definitions\nused here. The uncertainties for nu_max and <delta nu> due to differences in\nrealization noise are not negligible and should be taken into account when\nusing these results for stellar modelling.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Aug 2010 20:00:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-19"}
