cation mass scale of the ICMF and the fraction of clusters\nsuffering prompt dissolution. We infer truncation mass scales of <~ 10^6 M_sun\n(>~ 10^5 M_sun) without (with 90%) prompt dissolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Aug 2010 23:56:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Dec 2010 10:08:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-19"}
