oing this, we extend previous results of Krupa and Melbourne\n(1995,2004) and give criteria for simple heteroclinic cycles in $\\R^4$ to be\nMilnor attractors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Aug 2010 09:58:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 26 Feb 2011 17:48:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-19"}
