 We also find strong evidence for\nsystemic rotation in the globular clusters of M31 particularly for the most\nmetal-rich.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Aug 2010 10:23:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 Sep 2010 08:18:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-19"}
