 maximal value of the cutoff admitted within lattice\nElectroweak theory cannot exceed the value of the order of 1 TeV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Aug 2010 11:01:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Sep 2010 17:08:42 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 6 Sep 2010 06:41:58 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 9 Oct 2010 09:01:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-11-19"}
