ta2 ~ 7.4 +/- 0.3 meV. This corresponds to\neither the gaping of the electron and hole pockets, respectively, or an\nanisotropic s-wave gap on the electron pocket; both views are consistent with\nthe s+/- model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Aug 2010 14:49:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 25 Oct 2010 21:38:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-11-16"}
